name: Video Game Vulture
description:
The holder of the Video Game Vulture token will compete with Gary Vaynerchuk in person in a mutually agreed upon video game for one (1) hour per "year" (i.e.). Each year shall be defined as the twelve month time period commencing on May 6, 2021 and May 6, 2022. In no event shall any experience (including this experience) occur after May 5, 2024.

In other words, there are two (2) total redemptions occurring as follows:
- One (1) redemptions must occur between May 6, 2021 and May 5, 2022
- One (1) redemptions must occur between May 6, 2022 and May 5, 2023

This token is verifiable for admission to VeeCon 2022, 2023, 2024 

All access experiences will be pre-scheduled in advance with 90 day notice via a VeeFriends representative
